				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Just a guess, but there is a warven blacksmith in Raith Mts that asks for scales...<BR>
I know you get the really good breastplate and cloak for turning in the scales of the major dragons, but I believe he hints at there being more of them, he hangs out near the inn, by the druids, along with a gnome jeweler...<BR>
Hope this helps.<BR>
<BR>
Baslik, Enchanter of Xegony
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
</table><br>
